<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَنَارُهُ جَنَّةُ طُوبَى لِدَاخِلِهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَزُورُ جَنَّتِهِ نَارٌ مِنَ السُّعُرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شَهْرٌ وَعَشْرٌ لَيَإلى طُولَ مُدَّتِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَكِنَّهُ عَجَبٌ فِي الطُّولِ وَالْقِصَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَبْعَثُ اللهُ عِيسَى نَاصِرًا حَكَمًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عَدْلاً وَيَعْضِدُهُ بِالنَّصْرِ وَالظَّفَرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَيَتْبَعُ الْكَاذِبَ الْبَاغِي وَيَقْتُلُهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيَمْحَقُ اللهُ أَهْلَ الْبَغْي وَالضَّرَرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَقَامَ عِيسَى يُقِيمُ الْحَقَّ مُتَّبِعًا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>شَرِيعَةَ الْمُصْطَفَى الْمُخْتَارِ مِنْ مُضَرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فِي أَرْبَعِينَ مِنَ الأَعْوَامِ مُخْصِبَةٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَيَكْسِبُ الْمَالَ فِيهَا كُلُّ مُفْتَقِرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>حَتَّى إِذَا أَنْفَذَ اللهُ الْقَضَاءَ دَعَى<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عِيسَى فَأَفْنَاهُمُ الْمَوْلَى عَلَى قَدْرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَعَادَ لِلنَّاسِ عِيدُ الْخَيْرِ مُكْتَمِلاً<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>حَتَّى يَتِمَّ لِعِيسَى آخِرُ الْعُمُرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَالشَّمْسُ حِينَ تُرَى فِي الْغَرْبِ طَالِعَةً<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>طُلُوعُهَا آيَةٌ مِنْ أَعْظَمِ الْكِبَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَعِنْدَ ذَلِكَ لا إِيمَانَ يُقْبَلُ مِنْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَهْلِ الْجُحُودِ وَلا عُذْرٌ لِمُعْتَذِرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>